long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_GB,es,e:
Among Dash, the thrilling space-themed game, is now available as a Chrome Extension. Embark on an exciting interstellar adventure right from your Chrome browser. Navigate through treacherous obstacles and dodge enemy spacecraft as you strive to reach the highest score.

With the Among Dash Chrome Extension, you can experience the fast-paced gameplay and immersive space environment directly in your browser. Test your reflexes and agility as you maneuver your spaceship through challenging levels, collecting power-ups along the way.

Whether you're a fan of space games or enjoy action-packed challenges, the Chrome Extension version of Among Dash offers a convenient and accessible way to enjoy this captivating game. Get ready to dash through the cosmos and defy gravity in this thrilling game available at your fingertips.
